title: No Doom Bots or All Star Icon
body: I Beat Doom Bots the first weekend it was out and still havent got the lil devil teemo icon or the all star icon

replies.body:
The Teemoing Icons are being distributed until November 17th, so if you don't have it by then, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).

If you don't have the All Star Icon after *a week* has passed by from the time you locked in your picks, you should also submit a ticket so we can take care of you.
